race.comment: DESTINI PALADIN (8) was below best last time finishing seventh at this track, but prior to that had been racing well including a Grade 5 win two back at this track. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. DOWN SOUTH GIRL (1) was a winner (16.89) at this track two back but out of the placings last time when 8th at Shepparton. Form here at the trip sound including 10 wins. Should be about the money. EAGLES FLY ALONE (2) is worth a look over a shorter journey this time. Something for the Multiples: STILSON (6)
